(217, 54, 'ayebare.k.timothy@gmail.com', NULL, 'EMAIL', 'ALERT_CRITICAL', '🚨 CRITICAL · VHF HIGH CONFIDENCE · Ngoromoro · IHR Response Required', 'Critical Alert\n\n\n\n\nIHR · POE Sentinel · Ngoromoro\n🚨 CRITICAL ALERT\nVHF HIGH CONFIDENCE\n\n\nThis event matches CRITICAL-risk criteria under IHR 2005. Immediate clinical response, contact tracing, and POE emergency-protocol activation are required. Acknowledge within 4 hours.\n\nAlert Summary\nxsdhdwxhgswdgdhd\n\nAlert codeVHF_HIGH_CONFIDENCE\nRisk levelCRITICAL\nRouted toNATIONAL\nIHR tiernone\nDistrictLamwo District\n\nAcknowledge within 4h\nOpen POE Sentinel →\nWhy you\'re getting this: you are on the notifica', '<!DOCTYPE html><html lang=\"en\"><head><meta charset=\"utf-8\"><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width,initial-scale=1\"><title>Critical Alert</title></head><body style=\"margin:0;padding:0;background:#F0F4FA;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,&quot;Segoe UI&quot;,Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;color:#0F172A;\">\n<table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"background:#F0F4FA;padding:28px 12px;\"><tr><td align=\"center\">\n<table role=\"presentation\" width=\"600\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"max-width:600px;background:#FFFFFF;border-radius:14px;overflow:hidden;box-shadow:0 10px 40px -12px rgba(15,23,42,.18);\">\n<tr><td style=\"height:5px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,#DC2626 0%,#F59E0B 100%);\"></td></tr>\n<tr><td style=\"padding:28px 32px 18px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#7F1D1D 0%,#991B1B 55%,#001D3D 100%);\">\n<div style=\"font-size:10px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:2px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.75);text-transform:uppercase;\">IHR · POE Sentinel · Ngoromoro</div>\n<div style=\"font-size:26px;font-weight:900;letter-spacing:-.5px;color:#FFFFFF;margin-top:6px;line-height:1.18;\">🚨 CRITICAL ALERT</div>\n<div style=\"font-size:14px;color:#FEE2E2;font-weight:600;margin-top:4px;\">VHF HIGH CONFIDENCE</div>\n</td><