(242, 119, 'ecsahccloudsurveillancealerts@gmail.com', NULL, 'EMAIL', 'BREACH_717', '⏱ 7-1-7 BREACH · DEMO_183022 · MUTUKULA · root-cause due 24h', '\n  7 · 1 · 7 FRAMEWORK BREACH\n  Response stage missed — root-cause review required immediately.\n  ⏱ DEMO_183022 breached the 7-1-7 clock\n  Suspected VHF — returned traveller from DRC North Kivu\n\n\n\n  The global 7-1-7 target for outbreak response (7 days to detect, 1 day to notify, 7 days for effective early response) has been missed on this alert. This email is the breach notification for the record. A bottleneck review + root-cause analysis must be completed and attached to the alert in the cons', '<!DOCTYPE html><html><head><meta charset=\"utf-8\"><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width,initial-scale=1\"></head><body style=\"margin:0;padding:0;background:#EEF2F7;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;color:#0F172A;\"><table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"background:#EEF2F7;padding:24px 12px;\"><tr><td align=\"center\"><table role=\"presentation\" width=\"640\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"max-width:640px;background:#FFFFFF;border-radius:10px;overflow:hidden;box-shadow:0 4px 16px rgba(15,23,42,0.08);\"><tr><td style=\"background:linear-gradient(135deg,#000000 0%,#7F1D1D 60%,#991B1B 100%);padding:26px 28px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.22em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#FECACA;font-weight:700;\">7 · 1 · 7 FRAMEWORK BREACH</div>\n  <div style=\"margin-top:6px;font-size:12px;color:#FCA5A5;font-weight:600;\">Response stage missed — root-cause review required immediately.</div>\n  <div style=\"margin-top:12px;font-size:24px;font-weight:800;color:#FFFFFF;line-height:1.15;\">⏱ DEMO_183022 breached the 7-1-7 clock</div>\n  <div style=\"margin-top:8px;font-size:13px;color:#FECACA;\">Suspected VHF — returned traveller from DRC North Kivu</div>\n</td></tr>\n\n<tr><td style=\"padding:22px 28px 0;\">\n  <p style=\"margin:0;fo