(257, 119, 'ecsahccloudsurveillancealerts@gmail.com', NULL, 'EMAIL', 'FOLLOWUP_OVERDUE', '⊘ OVERDUE 5h · CASE_INVESTIGATION · DEMO_183022', '\n  OVERDUE · RTSL 14 action past its window\n  This is the escalation notice — supervisor copy appended.\n  ⊘ OVERDUE · Case investigation started\n  Overdue by 5 h (330 min) · was due 2026-04-21 13:30\n\n\n\n  An RTSL-14 early response action tied to DEMO_183022 is now overdue. The alert is exposed to the 7-1-7 breach clock; the supervisor copy is visible on this thread. Please take direct action now.\n\n\n\n  Overdue action\n  \n    CodeCASE_INVESTIGATION\n    LabelCase investigation started\n    Current sta', '<!DOCTYPE html><html><head><meta charset=\"utf-8\"><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width,initial-scale=1\"></head><body style=\"margin:0;padding:0;background:#EEF2F7;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;color:#0F172A;\"><table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"background:#EEF2F7;padding:24px 12px;\"><tr><td align=\"center\"><table role=\"presentation\" width=\"640\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"max-width:640px;background:#FFFFFF;border-radius:10px;overflow:hidden;box-shadow:0 4px 16px rgba(15,23,42,0.08);\"><tr><td style=\"background:linear-gradient(135deg,#7F1D1D 0%,#B91C1C 50%,#DB2777 100%);padding:24px 28px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#FBCFE8;font-weight:700;\">OVERDUE · RTSL 14 action past its window</div>\n  <div style=\"margin-top:6px;font-size:12px;color:#FCE7F3;\">This is the escalation notice — supervisor copy appended.</div>\n  <div style=\"margin-top:12px;font-size:22px;font-weight:800;color:#FFFFFF;line-height:1.2;\">⊘ OVERDUE · Case investigation started</div>\n  <div style=\"margin-top:8px;font-size:13px;color:#FBCFE8;\">Overdue by 5 h (330 min) · was due 2026-04-21 13:30</div>\n</td></tr>\n\n<tr><td style=\"padding:22px 28px 0;\">\n  <p style=\"margin:0;font-size:13p