(267, 118, 'vexa256@gmail.com', NULL, 'EMAIL', 'NATIONAL_INTELLIGENCE', '◉ Uganda intel · silent 0 · stuck 9 · overdue 1', '\n  Uganda · NATIONAL POE INTELLIGENCE BRIEF\n  Issued every 72 hours · IntelligenceEngine v1 · all POEs, all districts, all alerts.\n  ◉ National intelligence digest\n\n\n\n  UG national surveillance brief — 9 alert(s) are open past the acknowledgement SLA; 1 follow-up action(s) are overdue, some blocking closure; and 2 disease-by-district cluster signal(s) exceed the 14-day baseline. Each section below is actionable today.\n\n\n\n  1 · Silent POEs (no submission in the last 24h)\n  \n    0 POE(s) silent. A', '<!DOCTYPE html><html><head><meta charset=\"utf-8\"><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width,initial-scale=1\"></head><body style=\"margin:0;padding:0;background:#EEF2F7;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;color:#0F172A;\"><table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"background:#EEF2F7;padding:24px 12px;\"><tr><td align=\"center\"><table role=\"presentation\" width=\"640\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"max-width:640px;background:#FFFFFF;border-radius:10px;overflow:hidden;box-shadow:0 4px 16px rgba(15,23,42,0.08);\"><tr><td style=\"background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0C0A36 0%,#1E1B4B 50%,#1E40AF 100%);padding:26px 28px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.22em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#BFDBFE;font-weight:700;\">Uganda · NATIONAL POE INTELLIGENCE BRIEF</div>\n  <div style=\"margin-top:6px;font-size:12px;color:#DBEAFE;\">Issued every 72 hours · IntelligenceEngine v1 · all POEs, all districts, all alerts.</div>\n  <div style=\"margin-top:12px;font-size:22px;font-weight:800;color:#FFFFFF;line-height:1.2;\">◉ National intelligence digest</div>\n</td></tr>\n\n<tr><td style=\"padding:22px 28px 0;\">\n  <p style=\"margin:0;font-size:13px;color:#0F172A;\">UG national surveillance brief — 9 alert(s) are open past the acknowledgement SLA; 1 follow-up action(s) are overdue, some blocking closure; and 2 disease-by-district cluster signal(s) exceed the 14-day baseline. Each section below is actionable today.</p>\n</td></tr>\n\n<tr><td style=\"padding:16px 28px 0;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.08em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#1E40AF;font-weight:800;\">1 · Silent POEs (no submission in the last 24h)</div>\n  <div style=\"margin-top:8px;padding:12px 14px;background:#EFF6FF;border:1px solid #BFDBFE;border-radius:6px;\">\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 6px;font-size:12px;color:#1E3A8A;\"><strong>0 POE(s) silent.</strong> A silent POE either has no border traffic — or the duty officer is not logging.</p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0;color:#047857;font-size:12px;\">No silent POEs.</p>\n  </div>\n</td></tr>\n\n<tr><td style=\"padding:14px 28px 0;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.08em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#1E40AF;font-weight:800;\">2 · Unsubmitted pipelines (&gt;3 days unsynced)</div>\n  <div style=\"margin-top:8px;padding:12px 14px;background:#EFF6FF;border:1px solid #BFDBFE;border-radius:6px;\">\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 6px;font-size:12px;color:#1E3A8A;\"><strong>0 POE(s)</strong> have offline data that has not reached the server. This breaks country-wide visibility.</p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0;color:#047857;font-size:12px;\">All pipelines synced.</p>\n  </div>\n</td></tr>\n\n<tr><td style=\"padding:14px 28px 0;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.08em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#1E40AF;font-weight:800;\">3 · Dormant accounts (no login in the last 14 days)</div>\n  <div style=\"margin-top:8px;padding:12px 14px;background:#EFF6FF;border:1px solid #BFDBFE;border-radius:6px;\">\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 6px;font-size:12px;color:#1E3A8A;\"><strong>0 officer account(s)</strong> are dormant. Credential hygiene + roster refresh recommended.</p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0;color:#047857;font-size:12px;\">All officers logged in recently.</p>\n  </div>\n</td></tr>\n\n<tr><td s