; 1 follow-up action(s) are overdue, some blocking closure; and 2 disease-by-district cluster signal(s) exceed the 14-day baseline. Each section below is actionable today.</p>\n</td></tr>\n\n<tr><td style=\"padding:16px 28px 0;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.08em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#1E40AF;font-weight:800;\">1 · Silent POEs (no submission in the last 24h)</div>\n  <div style=\"margin-top:8px;padding:12px 14px;background:#EFF6FF;border:1px solid #BFDBFE;border-radius:6px;\">\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 6px;font-size:12px;color:#1E3A8A;\"><strong>0 POE(s) silent.</strong> A silent POE either has no border traffic — or the duty officer is not logging.</p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0;color:#047857;font-size:12px;\">No silent POEs.</p>\n  </div>\n</td></tr>\n\n<tr><td style=\"padding:14px 28px 0;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.08em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#1E40AF;font-weight:800;\">2 · Unsubmitted pipelines (&gt;3 days unsynced)</div>\n  <div style=\"margin-top:8px;padding:12px 14px;background:#EFF6FF;border:1px solid #BFDBFE;border-radius:6px;\">\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 6px;font-size:12px;color:#1E3A8A;\"><strong>0 POE(s)</strong> have offline data that has not reached the server. This breaks country-wide visibility.</p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0;color:#047857;font-size:12px;\">All pipelines synced.</p>\n  </div>\n</td></tr>\n\n<tr><td style=\"padding:14px 28px 0;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.08em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#1E40AF;font-weight:800;\">3 · Dormant accounts (no login in the last 14 days)</div>\n  <div style=\"margin-top:8px;padding:12px 14px;background:#EFF6FF;border:1px solid #BFDBFE;border-radius:6px;\">\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 6px;font-size:12px;color:#1E3A8A;\"><strong>0 officer account(s)</strong> are dormant. Credential hygiene + roster refresh recommended.</p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0;color:#047857;font-size:12px;\">All officers logged in recently.</p>\n  </div>\n</td></tr>\n\n<tr><td style=\"padding:14px 28px 0;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.08em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#1E40AF;font-weight:800;\">4 · Stuck alerts (open &gt;SLA · not acknowledged)</div>\n  <div style=\"margin-top:8px;padding:12px 14px;background:#EFF6FF;border:1px solid #BFDBFE;border-radius:6px;\">\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 6px;font-size:12px;color:#B91C1C;font-weight:700;\">9 alert(s) stuck.</p>\n    <ul style=\"margin:0;padding-left:18px;font-size:13px;\"><li style=\"margin:4px 0;\"><strong>TIER1_ALWAYS_CRITICAL</strong> · CRITICAL · POE Ngoromoro<br><span style=\"color:#64748B;font-size:11px;\">TIER1 ALWAYS CRITICAL · opened 2026-04-21 00:29:40</span></li><li style=\"margin:4px 0;\"><strong>TIER1_ALWAYS_CRITICAL</strong> · CRITICAL · POE Ngoromoro<br><span style=\"color:#64748B;font-size:11px;\">TIER1 ALWAYS CRITICAL · opened 2026-04-21 00:29:41</span></li><li style=\"margin:4px 0;\"><strong>TIER1_ALWAYS_CRITICAL</strong> · CRITICAL · POE Ngoromoro<br><span style=\"color:#64748B;font-size:11px;\">TIER1 ALWAYS CRITICAL · opened 2026-04-21 00:29:41</span></li><li style=\"margin:4px 0;\"><strong>VHF_HIGH_CONFIDENCE</strong> · CRITICAL · POE Ngoromoro<br><span style=\"color:#64748B;font-size:11px;\">VHF HIGH CONFIDENCE · opened 2026-04-21 00:29:42</span></li><li style=\"margin:4px 0;\"><strong>TIER1_ALWAYS_CRITICAL</strong> · CRITICAL · POE Ngoromoro<br><span style=\"color:#64748B;font-size:11px;\">TIER1 ALWAYS CRITICAL · opened 2026-04-21 00:29:42</span></li><li style=\"margin:4px 0;\"><strong>TIER1_ALWAYS_CRITICAL</strong> · CRITICAL · POE Ngoromoro<br><span style=\"color:#64748B;font-size:11px;\">TIER1 ALWAYS CRITICAL · opened 2026-04-21 00:29:43</span></li><li style=\"margin:4px 0;\"><strong>TIER1_ALWAYS_CRITICAL</strong> · CRITICAL · POE Ngoromoro<br><span style=\"color:#64748B;font-size:11px;\">TIER1 ALWAYS CRITICAL · opened 2026-04-21 00:29:43</span></li><li style=\"margin:4px 0;\"><strong>TIER1_ALWAYS_CRITICAL</strong> · CRITICAL · POE Ngoromoro<br><span style=\"color:#64748B;font-size:11px;\">TIER1 ALWAYS CRITICAL · opened 2026-04-21 00:29:44</span></li><li style=\"margin:4px 0;\"><strong>VHF_HIGH_CONFIDENCE</strong> · CRITICAL · POE Ngoromoro<br><span style=\"color:#64748B;font-size:11px;\">VHF HIGH CONFIDENCE · opened 2026-04-21 14:27:40</span></li></ul>\n  </div>\n</td></tr>\n\n<tr><td style=\"padding:14px 28px 0;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.08em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#1E40AF;font-weight:800;\">5 · Overdue follow-ups (blocking closure)</div>\n  <div style=\"margin-top:8px;padding:12px 14px;background:#EFF6FF;border:1px solid #BFDBFE;border-radius:6px;\">\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 6px;font-size:12px;color:#B91C1C;font-weight:700;\">1 follow-up action(s) past their window.</p>\n    <ul style=\"margin:0;padding-left:18px;font-size:13px;\"><li style=\"margin:4px 0;\"><strong>[CASE_INVESTIGATION]</strong> Case investigation started · alert DEMO_183022 · due 2026-04-21 13:30:22 · <span style=\"color:#B91C1C;\">blocks closure</span></li></ul>\n  </div>\n</td></tr>\n\n<tr><td style=\"padding:14px 28px 0;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.08em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#1E40AF;font-weight:800;\">6 · Case spikes &amp; cluster signals</div>\n  <div style=\"margin-top:8px;padding:12px 14px;background:#EFF6FF;border:1px solid #BFDBFE;border-radius:6px;\">\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 6px;font-size:12px;color:#1E3A8A;\"><strong>2</strong> anomalies detected vs. rolling 14-day baseline.</p>\n    <ul style=\"margin:0;padding-left:18px;font-size:13px;\"><li style=\"margin:4px 0;\"><strong>cchf</strong> in district <strong>Lamwo District</strong> — 2 cases/24h vs. 0.07/day 14d baseline</li><li style=\"margin:4px 0;\"><strong>lassa_fever</strong> in district <strong>Lamwo District</strong> — 2 cases/24h vs. 0.00/day 14d baseline</li></ul>\n  </div>\n</td></tr>\n\n<tr><td style=\"padding:14px 28px 0;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.08em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#1E40AF;font-weight:800;\">7 · Executive read-out &amp; recommendations</div>\n  <ul style=\"margin:8px 0 0 20px;padding:0;font-size:13px;color:#0F172A;\">\n    <li style=\"margin:5px 0;\">Reach out to every silent POE listed above within 24h.</li>\n    <li style=\"margin:5px 0;\">Contact officers from dormant accounts; confirm roster is correct.</li>\n    <li style=\"margin:5px 0;\">Re-assign ownership for stuck alerts and overdue follow-ups.</li>\n    <li style=\"margin:5px 0;\">Investigate any cluster signal — contact DHO of the affected district.</li>\n    <li style=\"margin:5px 0;\">Verify Annex 2 pipeline works end-to-end — any suspected Tier 1 event must be notified to WHO within 24h.</li>\n  </ul>\n</td></tr>\n\n<tr><td style=\"padding:20px 28px 14px;\">\n  <div style=\"background:#1E40AF;border-radius:8px;padding:14px 16px;text-align:center;\">\n    <a href=\"http://localhost/#/intelligence\" style=\"color:#FFFFFF;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;text-decoration:none;\">Open national intelligence console →</a>\n  </div>\n</td></tr>\n<tr><td style=\"padding:18px 28px 14px;background:#F1F5F9;border-top:1px solid #E2E8F0;\">\n  <p style=\"margin:0;font-size:11px;color:#475569;line-height:1.5;\">\n    <strong>Uganda POE Sentinel</strong> · INTELLIGENCE · EVERY 72h · WHO IHR 2005 + AFRO IDSR 2021 + 7-1-7 framework.<br>\n    Digest generated 2026-04-21 18:30 for window ending 2026-04-21.<br>\n    Open dashboard → <a href=\"http://localhost/#/intelligence\" style=\"color:#1D4ED8;text-decoration:none;font-weight:600;\">http://localhost/#/intelligence</a>\n  </p>\n</td></tr></table></td></tr></table></body></html>', 'ALERT', 21, 'UG', 'KYOTERA', 'MUTUKULA', 'SENT', NULL, 0, '2026-04-21 18:31:42', NULL, NULL, 'CMD:demo-all', '2026-04-21 18:31:42', '2026-04-21 18:31:42'),
(270, NULL, 'vexa256@gmail.com', NULL, 'EMAIL', 'AUTH_NEW_LOGIN_DEVICE', 'POE Sentinel · New sign-in on Browser · Unknown OS', NULL, '<!DOCTYPE html><html><head><meta charset=\"utf-8\"><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width,initial-scale=1\"></head><body style=\"margin:0;padding:0;background:#EEF2F7;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;color:#0F172A;\"><table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"background:#EEF2F7;padding:24px 12px;\"><tr><td align=\"center\"><table role=\"presentation\" width=\"600\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"max-width:600px;background:#FFFFFF;border-radius:10px;overflow:hidden;box-shadow:0 4px 16px rgba(15,23,42,0.08);\"><tr><td style=\"background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0369a1 0%,#0284c7 55%,#0ea5e9 100%);padding:24px 28px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#bae6fd;font-weight:700;\">POE Sentinel · New sign-in</div>\n  <div style=\"margin-top:10px;font-size:22px;font-weight:800;color:#fff;\">Sign-in from a new device</div>\n</td></tr>\n<tr><td style=\"padding:22px 28px 0;font-size:13px;\">\n  <p style=\"margin:0 0 10px;\">Hello Ayebare Timothy,</p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0 0 10px;\">Your account was signed in from a device we haven\'t seen in the last 30 days.</p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0 0 10px;\"><strong>Device:</strong> Browser · Unknown OS</p>\n</td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding:14px 28px 0;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.08em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#475569;font-weight:700;\">Device + location</div>\n  <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin-top:6px;background:#F8FAFC;border:1px solid #E2E8F0;border-radius:8px;\">\n    <tr><td style=\"padding:6px 12px;font-size:12px;color:#475569;\">IP address</td><td style=\"padding:6px 12px;text-align:right;font-size:12px;font-family:ui-monospace,monospace;\">127.0.0.1</td></tr>\n    <tr><td style=\"padding:6px 12px;font-size:12px;color:#475569;\">User agent</td><td style=\"padding:6px 12px;text-align:right;font-size:12px;\">curl/8.5.0</td></tr>\n    <tr><td style=\"padding:6px 12px;font-size:12px;color:#475569;\">Time (UTC)</td><td style=\"padding:6px 12px;text-align:right;font-size:12px;\">2026-04-21 21:12</td></tr>\n  </table>\n</td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding:16px 28px;background:#F1F5F9;border-top:1px solid #E2E8F0;\">\n  <p style=\"margin:0;font-size:11px;color:#475569;line-height:1.55;\">\n    <strong>POE Sentinel</strong> · New sign-in notice<br>\n    If this wasn\'t you, contact your administrator immediately and reset your password.<br>\n    Generated 2026-04-21 21:12 UTC from 127.0.0.1.\n  </p>\n</td></tr></table></td></tr></table></body></html>', 'USER', 6, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'SENT', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'AUTH:mailer', '2026-04-21 21:12:58', '2026-04-21 21:12:58'),
(271, NULL, 'vexa256@gmail.com', NULL, 'EMAIL', 'AUTH_PASSWORD_RESET', 'Reset your POE Sentinel password', NULL, '<!DOCTYPE html><html><head><meta charset=\"utf-8\"><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width,initial-scale=1\"></head><body style=\"margin:0;padding:0;background:#EEF2F7;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;color:#0F172A;\"><table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"background:#EEF2F7;padding:24px 12px;\"><tr><td align=\"center\"><table role=\"presentation\" width=\"600\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"max-width:600px;background:#FFFFFF;border-radius:10px;overflow:hidden;box-shadow:0 4px 16px rgba(15,23,42,0.08);\"><tr><td style=\"background:linear-gradient(135deg,#b45309 0%,#d97706 55%,#f59e0b 100%);padding:24px 28px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#fef3c7;font-weight:700;\">POE Sentinel · Password reset</div>\n  <div style=\"margin-top:10px;font-size:22px;font-weight:800;color:#fff;\">Reset your password</div>\n</td></tr>\n<tr><td style=\"padding:22px 28px 0;font-size:13px;\">\n  <p style=\"margin:0 0 10px;\">Hello Master Administrator,</p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0 0 10px;\">We received a request to reset the password for <strong>vexa256@gmail.com</strong>. Click below to pick a new password. This link is valid for <strong>2 hours</strong>.</p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0 0 10px;color:#92400E;\"><strong>Didn\'t request this?</strong> Ignore this email — your password will not change.</p>\n</td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding:18px 28px 10px;\">\n  <div style=\"background:#b45309;border-radius:8px;padding:14px 16px;text-align:center;\">\n    <a href=\"http://localhost/reset-password?token=a6525c7d790b5261132fe0a9d7d70fe564b6d3891a0295d67d56026d09a25b15&amp;email=vexa256%40gmail.com\" style=\"color:#FFFFFF;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;text-decoration:none;\">Reset password →</a>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin:10px 0 0;font-size:11px;color:#64748B;text-align:center;\">Or paste this link into your browser:<br><span style=\"word-break:break-all;\">http://localhost/reset-password?token=a6525c7d790b5261132fe0a9d7d70fe564b6d3891a0295d67d56026d09a25b15&amp;email=vexa256%40gmail.com</span></p>\n</td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding:14px 28px 0;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.08em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#475569;font-weight:700;\">Device + location</div>\n  <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin-top:6px;background:#F8FAFC;border:1px solid #E2E8F0;border-radius:8px;\">\n    <tr><td style=\"padding:6px 12px;font-size:12px;color:#475569;\">IP address</td><td style=\"padding:6px 12px;text-align:right;font-size:12px;font-family:ui-monospace,monospace;\">127.0.0.1</td></tr>\n    <tr><td style=\"padding:6px 12px;font-size:12px;color:#475569;\">User agent</td><td style=\"padding:6px 12px;text-align:right;font-size:12px;\"></td></tr>\n    <tr><td style=\"padding:6px 12px;font-size:12px;color:#475569;\">Time (UTC)</td><td style=\"padding:6px 12px;text-align:right;font-size:12px;\">2026-04-21 21:58</td></tr>\n  </table>\n</td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding:16px 28px;background:#F1F5F9;border-top:1px solid #E2E8F0;\">\n  <p style=\"margin:0;font-size:11px;color:#475569;line-height:1.55;\">\n    <strong>POE Sentinel</strong> · Password reset request<br>\n    If this wasn\'t you, contact your administrator immediately and reset your password.<br>\n    Generated 2026-04-21 21:58 UTC from 127.0.0.1.\n  </p>\n</td></tr></table></td></tr></table></body></html>', 'USER', 6, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'SENT', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'AUTH:mailer', '2026-04-21 21:58:33', '2026-04-21 21:58:33');

